general.name: asQA
general.description:
Quality analysis diagnostic output from a single astrometric pipeline run.
If the input FANG files came from SSC, then the "sscXX_id" keys are present
but not the "psXX_id"; vice versa if the input FANG files came from PS.
general.naming_convention: asQA-rrrrrr.fit, where rrrrrr is the imaging run number.

changelog.description: Describes changes to the datamodel product and/or file structure from one release to another
